        <mxCell id="footnoteBox" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#444444;" value="Entities assumed in the original ask but NOT present as separate tables" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="1600" x="120" y="660" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="footnoteText" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="• Widget — apps/widget is a static Vite/IIFE bundle, not a DB-backed resource. A &quot;widget&quot; is really a Project&#39;s public submission endpoint, identified by Project.apiKey + domain whitelist.&#xa;• FeedbackAnalysis — AI results (sentimentScore, category, aiSummary, tags) are columns directly on Feedback, written by AiProcessor after the Gemini call (see Request Lifecycle tab) — no separate table.&#xa;• Subscription — billing/plan fields (plan, planStatus, planUpdatedAt, stripeCustomerId, stripeSubscriptionId, stripePriceId, trialEndsAt, lastStripeEventAt) are columns directly on Team (moved from User 2026-07-05, migration 1774910000000-TeamAsTenant). Billing is per-team (the tenant), not per-user or per-project.&#xa;• API Key — two distinct concepts exist as plain columns, not a table: User.apiKey (nullable, unique — user-level) and Project.apiKey (unique, required — used by the widget to authenticate public feedback submissions)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="115" width="1560" x="140" y="695" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram id="reg-onboarding" name="Registration &amp; Onboarding Flow">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1147" dy="1050" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1900" pageHeight="1200" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="regTitle" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;align=left;" value="InsightStream AI — Registration &amp; Onboarding Flow (verified 2026-07-01; auth/tenant labels synced 2026-07-05)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="1350" x="20" y="10" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regPanelLanding" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="apps/landing — insightstream.ai (Vercel, port 3002, zero @insightstream/* deps)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="285" x="20" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regLandingHome" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="/ — Homepage&#xa;Hero: &quot;Get Started Free&quot; → /auth/register&#xa;Nav: &quot;Get Started&quot; → /auth/register&#xa;Pricing: &quot;Start 14-day Trial&quot;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="85" width="245" x="40" y="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regLandingQuiz" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="/quiz — Interactive Quiz&#xa;Result → APP_URL/?plan={plan}&#xa;(plan param: UI pre-selection only,&#xa;not server-enforced)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="85" width="245" x="40" y="210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regPanelWeb" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="apps/web — app.insightstream.ai (Vercel, port 3000)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="285" x="345" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regWebRegister" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="/auth/register&#xa;Email + Password form&#xa;OR: &quot;Continue with Google&quot;&#xa;OR: &quot;Continue with GitHub&quot;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="245" x="365" y="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regWebDashboard" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="/dashboard&#xa;(redirect after successful&#xa;registration + login)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="245" x="365" y="220" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regPanelApi" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="apps/api — AuthService.register() flow" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="560" width="420" x="670" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="① POST /auth/register&#xa;(public endpoint — no auth guard)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="380" x="690" y="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="② isEmailAllowed(email)&#xa;invite-only guard → 403 ForbiddenException if blocked" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="55" width="380" x="690" y="165" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep3" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="③ findOneByEmail(email)&#xa;duplicate check → 409 ConflictException if exists" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="55" width="380" x="690" y="235" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep4" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="④ bcrypt.hash(password, 10)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="380" x="690" y="305" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep5" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="⑤ usersService.create({email, passwordHash})&#xa;INSERT INTO users (role: user)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="55" width="380" x="690" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep6" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="⑥ teamsService.ensurePersonalTeam(userId)&#xa;INSERT INTO teams (plan: free default) + INSERT INTO team_members (role: owner)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="380" x="690" y="430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regStep7" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;" value="⑦ login(user) → jwtService.sign({sub, email, role})&#xa;returns { access_token, user } — expiresIn: 7d" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="55" width="380" x="690" y="505" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regPanelDb" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" value="PostgreSQL — writes on registration" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="560" width="240" x="1130" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regDbUsers" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" value="users&#xa;email, passwordHash&#xa;role: user" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="65" width="200" x="1150" y="360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regDbTeams" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" value="teams&#xa;name: Personal, ownerId&#xa;plan: free (billing lives here)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="55" width="200" x="1150" y="440" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regDbTeamMembers" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" value="team_members&#xa;userId, teamId, role: owner" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="55" width="200" x="1150" y="510" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regOauthPanel" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#666666;dashed=1;" value="OAuth Registration Path (alternative to password)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="195" width="650" x="20" y="355" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regOauthText" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="GET /auth/google|github → Passport OAuth strategy → provider callback&#xa;→ findByProviderId(id): if found → login() directly&#xa;→ findByEmail(email): if email matches existing user → auto-link accounts → login()&#xa;→ if new user: usersService.create({email, googleId|githubId}) → login()&#xa;&#xa;✔ Both register() and oauthLogin() call the idempotent ensurePersonalTeam()&#xa;   (hardened 2026-07-03, PLAN #2) — no teamless OAuth users.&#xa;&#xa;Callback redirect: ${FRONTEND_URL}/auth/oauth/callback?token={access_token}" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="165" width="610" x="40" y="380" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regResponsePanel" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#444444;" value="Response &amp; Token Storage" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="125" width="1080" x="20" y="640" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regResponseText" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="API returns: { access_token: &quot;eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...&quot;, user: { id, email, role } }&#xa;Web app stores Bearer token — sent as Authorization header on all subsequent API requests.&#xa;Redirect to /dashboard. Token expiry: 7 days. No refresh token. No server-side revocation (stateless JWT — same as login path)." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="1040" x="40" y="670" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regNotesPanel" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=6;fillColor=none;strokeColor=#444444;" value="Implementation Notes" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="710" width="430" x="1410" y="60" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regNotesText" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="• isEmailAllowed(): invite-only guard — throws 403 ForbiddenException if email domain or address not in allowlist. Restricts public signups.&#xa;&#xa;• Personal Team auto-creation: every password-registered user auto-gets a personal team (role: owner) at step ⑥, before login(). Cannot be skipped.&#xa;&#xa;• OAuth team parity: both register() and oauthLogin() call the idempotent ensurePersonalTeam() (hardened 2026-07-03, PLAN #2) — the earlier &quot;OAuth gap&quot; note is obsolete.&#xa;&#xa;• No email verification: registration immediately returns a valid JWT. No pending/unverified user state.&#xa;&#xa;• plan on registration: the personal team defaults to plan: free — billing lives on teams since 2026-07-05 (Team-as-Tenant); plan is no longer in the JWT or login response. The ?plan= query param from the Quiz is a UI pre-selection only — NOT applied server-side during POST /auth/register.&#xa;&#xa;• apps/landing has zero @insightstream/* package deps. Pure Next.js 16 + TailwindCSS + framer-motion + PostHog. No API calls from landing — all CTAs are plain &lt;a href&gt; links to app.insightstream.ai.&#xa;&#xa;• Landing port 3002 (dev), insightstream.ai (prod). Web port 3000 (dev), app.insightstream.ai (prod). Both deployed to Vercel, independently." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="650" width="390" x="1430" y="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regELandingCta" edge="1" parent="1" source="regLandingHome" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.4;" target="regWebRegister" value="CTA click">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regEWebApi" edge="1" parent="1" source="regWebRegister" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=1;exitY=0.5;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;" target="regStep1" value="submit form">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regEStep12" edge="1" parent="1" source="regStep1" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" target="regStep2">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regEStep23" edge="1" parent="1" source="regStep2" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" target="regStep3">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regEStep34" edge="1" parent="1" source="regStep3" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" target="regStep4">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="regEStep45" edge="1" parent="1" source="regStep4" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;html=1;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;" target="regStep5">
